reviewText: Totally satisfied with this item. Would recommend seller.
This little tale broke after many viewings and couldn't be found on DVD to upgrade. That said, the little girl is ecstatic to have her story viewable again!

This video, although short, is fun and creative claymation. If you have littles ones, they will enjoy the colorful characters. The adults may very well appreciate the amount of time this type of video takes to create. We sure do!
